Syria Releases Most of Banias Detainees, Al Watan Reports

-- B y   L i n a   I b r a h i m
-- 
2011-04-14T10:42:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/syria-releases-most-of-banias-detainees-al-watan-reports.html
Syrian authorities released most of
the people detained during recent unrest in the coastal city of
Banias,  Al Watan newspaper  said, citing a statement by nine
unidentified Syrian human rights groups.  Government officials said only prisoners who fired at
security forces or took part in armed operations would be held
in detention, without specifying how many people were released,
the newspaper said. Syrian authorities detained about 200 armed
people on April 12, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lina Ibrahim in Dubai at  librahim4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Riad Hamade at   rhamade@bloomberg.net . 